ğŸ“Š Key Results

- 68% of learners preferred short-duration skill-based courses.
- Mobile learning usage grew by 35% in two years.
- Gamified and interactive content improved completion rates by 40%.
- Coursera had the highest engagement, while Udemy offered the most flexibility.

